By Wes Rucker / govols247.com 
Three-star wing Jalen Johnson from North Carolina committed to Tennessee on Sunday, according to a tweet from the player himself. 
"I am excited to announce that I have committed to play basketball at the University of Tennessee," Johnson tweeted Sunday night. Read or Share this story: http://on.wbir.com/1RBAaMh TOP VIDEOS
